README file for tvpowerd

This catalogue has one optional daemon that is meant to be run on a separate
physical server than tvpvrd. The purpose of this daemon is to control the
power of the recording daemon. This means that it will communicate with the
tvpvrd daemon and shut down the server when no recroding is taking place.

This will help save eneryg.

Since this is supposed to be running on a sepaate server no installation can
be performed automatically. Follow these steps to install the dameon.

0. Copy the entire content of this directory to the server where you which to
install this daemon

1. Run (as root)

$>sh install.sh

This will install the daemon and documentation.
Note:  The installation will preseve any existing configuretion scripts.


